def _get_grouper(
    obj,
    key=None,
    axis=0,
    level=None,
    sort=True,
    observed=False,
    mutated=False,
    validate=True,
):
    group_axis = obj._get_axis(axis)

    if level is not None:
        # Handle the case when key is a list of keys
        if isinstance(key, list):
            groupings = [
                Grouping(
                    group_axis,
                    k,
                    obj=obj,
                    level=level,
                    sort=sort,
                    observed=observed,
                    in_axis=True,
                )
                for k in key
            ]
        else:
            # For a single key
            groupings = [
                Grouping(
                    group_axis,
                    key,
                    obj=obj,
                    level=level,
                    sort=sort,
                    observed=observed,
                    in_axis=True,
                )
            ]
    else:
        # Handle the case when key is a list of keys
        if isinstance(key, list):
            groupings = [
                Grouping(
                    group_axis,
                    k,
                    obj=obj,
                    level=level,
                    sort=sort,
                    observed=observed,
                    in_axis=True,
                )
                for k in key
            ]
        else:
            groupings = [
                Grouping(
                    group_axis,
                    key,
                    obj=obj,
                    level=level,
                    sort=sort,
                    observed=observed,
                    in_axis=True,
                )
            ]

    if len(groupings) == 0 and len(obj):
        raise ValueError("No group keys passed!")
    elif len(groupings) == 0:
        groupings.append(Grouping(Index([], dtype="int"), np.array([], dtype=np.intp)))

    grouper = BaseGrouper(group_axis, groupings, sort=sort, mutated=mutated)
    return grouper, [], obj
